SUMMARY:St. Baldrick's Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Since 2008\, the head-shaving extravaganza hosted at Annie Bailey’s Irish Public House has raised over $1 MILLION in support of the St. Baldrick’s Foundation’s ongoing fight to end childhood cancers. Whether you decide to #bravetheshave yourself\, volunteer your hair-cutting services as a shaver\, or support by making a donation\, we hope you’ll join us in helping to give hope to infants\, children\, teens & young adults fighting cancer!\n\nShaving starts at 12pm and ends at 3pm\, don’t miss your opportunity to support! \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Learn More
