SUMMARY:Etiquette Dinner Theater at The Log Cabin
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive dining experience where a 4-course meal is paired with live interactive theater. As you dine\, actors humorously demonstrate proper (and improper) table manners through a playful story featuring rival etiquette experts and their eager students. With light audience participation and plenty of laughs\, the night blends refinement and fun into one unforgettable experience.\n\nThis event will be available on multiple dates but for a limited number of guests so book soon!\n\nDates: April 16\, 17\, 22\, 23\, 24\nLocation: The Log Cabin restaurant\, 11 Lehoy Forest Dr\, Leola\, PA 17540 \nTickets: EARLY BIRD $95 through March 15th | $120 after\n\nLearn more and purchase tickets at https://logcabin1933.com/etiquette-dinner/ \n            \n        \n                \n            \n                \n                \n    Buy Tickets
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/etiquette-dinner-theater/
LOCATION:The Log Cabin Restaurant\, 11 Lehoy Forest Dr\, Leola\, 17540
CATEGORIES:Food & Drink
